Dudley Dickerson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dudley_Dickerson 0 Dudley Dickerson (November 27, 1906 – September 23, 1968) was an American film actor. Born in Chickasha, Oklahoma, he appeared in nearly 160 films between 1932 and 1952, and is best remembered for his roles in several Three Stooges films.
